<template>
    <v-sheet
        class="mb-3 secondary elevation-0"
        outlined>
        <v-form>
            <v-data-table
                :headers="headers"
                :items="channels">

            </v-data-table>
        </v-form>
    </v-sheet>
</template>
<script>
export default {
    data() {
        return {
            headers: [
                {
                    text: 'Dessert (100g serving)',
                    align: 'start',
                    sortable: false,
                    value: 'name',
                },
                { text: 'Calories', value: 'calories' },
                { text: 'Fat (g)', value: 'fat' },
                { text: 'Carbs (g)', value: 'carbs' },
                { text: 'Protein (g)', value: 'protein' },
                { text: 'Iron (%)', value: 'iron' },
            ],
        }
    },
    computed: {
        channels: {
            get() {
                return this.$store.channels
            }
        }
    }

}
</script>
